    "text": "DemocracyCorps Act\n\nThis bill creates the DemocracyCorps, a government corporation that must assist states and local governments with administering elections. The bill also establishes special election procedures for the 2020 federal elections, particularly with respect to COVID-19 preparedness, and revises certain election procedures for all federal elections."
